---
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-stone-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-zinc-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border border-blue-900/20 dark:border-blue-800/30 scroll-reveal">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-900 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300">
          זמין עכשיו • תגובה מיידית
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-4">
        מוכנים לפתור את הבעיות האלו?
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        דברו איתנו כדי להתחיל לעשות סדר בעסק שלכם.
      </p>
      
      <div class="space-y-3 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="שם פרטי" 
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-stone-300 dark:border-zinc-700 focus:border-blue-900 dark:focus:border-blue-700 focus:outline-none text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 placeholder-stone-400 dark:placeholder-zinc-500 transition-all"
          />
          <input 
            type="text" 
            placeholder="שם משפחה" 
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-stone-300 dark:border-zinc-700 focus:border-blue-900 dark:focus:border-blue-700 focus:outline-none text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 placeholder-stone-400 dark:placeholder-zinc-500 transition-all"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <input 
            type="tel" 
            placeholder="050-000-0000" 
            class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border-2 border-stone-300 dark:border-zinc-700 focus:border-blue-900 dark:focus:border-blue-700 focus:outline-none text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 placeholder-stone-400 dark:placeholder-zinc-500 transition-all"
            dir="ltr"
          />
          <button class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-900 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all transform hover:scale-105 whitespace-nowrap">
            דברו איתי 🤖
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-6">
        <span class="text-sm text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400">
          תגובה מיידית ⚡
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .scroll-reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.85) translateY(15px);
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .scroll-reveal.revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
  }
</style>